data.title: Buy tickets for EDEN MUÑOZ, COMO EN LOS VIEJOS TIEMPOS at Robarts Arena
data.meta_description: Don't miss EDEN MUÑOZ, COMO EN LOS VIEJOS TIEMPOS at Robarts Arena, Sarasota, FL. Get your tickets for August 31, 2024 at 8:00 on Ticketón.
data.text:
Edén Muñoz, known for being the leader and founder of the band Calibre 50, is a prominent Mexican singer, songwriter, and music producer. He started his career in music as part of the band Colmillo Norteño in 2006, releasing albums such as "El Cid" (2008) and "Sueño Guajiro" (2009). In 2010, Muñoz founded Calibre 50, reaching significant successes. However, in early 2022, he decided to leave the band to embark on a solo career. In February 2022, he released his second single, "Chale", which quickly reached prominent positions on the music charts along with his new hits. The next August 31 in Tampa do not miss his concert at Robarts Arena and ensure your place by buying your tickets here at Ticketón before they run out!

Doors open: 8:00 p.m.

All ages
